Zoom appearances. Defendant in custody. 
GUILTY pleas entered to Count 4 - Possess Drug Paraphernalia
with the repeater enhancer deleted, and Count 3 - Possession
of THC 2nd & Subsequent. Convicted. Counts 1 and 2 dismissed 
and read-in.  Sentence withheld. Defendant placed on probation 
to DOC for two (2) years. Conditions of probations:
1)	Maintain absolute sobriety
2)	Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
3)	Pay supervision fees in the amount to be determined by DOC;
4)	Pay costs of action;
5)	AODA assessment and follow through;
6)	Maintain full-time employment/schooling, combination;
7)	Submit DNA sample.
Count 4 - Defendant is sentenced to thirty (30) days jail, to run concurrent to the sentence defendant is presently serving.
